Source: pgcalendar
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/h4kbas/pgcalendar

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-pgcalendar
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-pgcalendar
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, postgresql-PGVERSION
Description: Infinite calendar and recurring schedule extension for PostgreSQL
  pgcalendar provides recurring schedules, projections, and exception handling
  as a pure SQL extension for PostgreSQL.
